snippet.title: Best VGM 1011 - Dragon Quest V - Monsters in the Dungeon
snippet.description:
Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sNqZidSXMVM

See also:
Best VGM 493 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m2Vlxyd9Wjw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Dragon Quest V (1992)
Monsters in the Dungeon
Koichi Sugiyama
